Repeat: P2, slip next stitch to dpn and hold in front; k2, then k1 from dpn; slip next 2 stitches to dpn and hold in back; k1, then k2 from dpn; p2
P2, k2, k2 tog but do not slip from needle; insert right-hand needle between the stitches just knitted together and knit the first stitch again; then slip both stitches from needle together; k2, p2
